messages.text: Hi my fellow cucumbers! My name is FlyingCucumber11. I am looking forward to learning more about Chatty Cucumbers. What is a chatty cucumber exactly?
Hi, flycingcucumber11! Good question! I personally thought this was a dating app for cucumbers. If that's the case, can someone send me the link for viewing profiles because I can't find it?
I'm pretty sure this is NOT a dating app! Gross!

Uh-oh! I thought I signed up for coding cucumbers. My parents are going to freak! If my parents find this message board, please know that I thought I signed up for a coding app for kids. I had no idea this was a dating app.
Hi, I'm ChattyCucumber19, and for the last time... I do NOT know what Chatty Cucumbers is. Can someone show me how to change my username. I'm over it.
